Subject: MrEd PPC requires the NavigationLib which is part of OS 8.5 and later thus making MrEd PPC incompatible with earlier system software. 

>Number:         1063
>Category:       mred
>Synopsis:       MrEd PPC requires the NavigationLib which is part of OS 8.5 and later thus making MrEd PPC incompatible with earlier system software.
>Confidential:   no
>Severity:       critical
>Priority:       high
>Responsible:    mflatt
>State:          closed
